OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fmostly dry with bright then some clear
OL,7,Fspells in the east. Cloudy with rain
OL,8,Fat times in the west, spreading east
OL,9,Flater.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FCloudy with patchy rain in the
OL,12,Fwest at first otherwise mostly dry
OL,13,Fwith bright spells and the odd inland
OL,14,Fafternoon shower.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,17,Fdry and bright Monday then cloudy with
OL,18,Fpatchy rain and showers Tuesday. Dry
OL,19,Fat first Wednesday then cloud and rain
OL,20,Fspread east later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
